column2: Understand the preliminary scope statement for the statewide email system and ensure that requirements remain within scope.

Specification must be complete 
within 6 weeks (30 business days).
Workgroup will use the 2006 Messaging Optimization Workgroup Survey as a basis for the 2009 Enterprise e-mail survey.

Specification must be complete and detailed enough to submit to outside vendors as Request For Information (RFI) or Request For 
Proposals (RFP) or an Invitation to Negotiate (ITN).

Specification must include an attachment which provides a narrative and breakdown of existing agency resources (personnel, equipment ? 
including storage capabilities, software-licenses) and current spend (reuse IV-C data where applicable) on e-mail.
